  "prompt": "Do any of the Indian banks provide personalized gift cards where I can put a personalized image on the card?",
  "response": "Several Indian banks offer personalized credit or debit cards with custom images. Here are a few examples:\n\n1. HDFC Bank: Offers personalized photo debit cards where you can upload your own image.\n\n2. ICICI Bank: Provides personalized debit cards with custom images.\n\n3. Axis Bank: Allows customers to customize their debit cards with personal photos.\n\n4. SBI Bank: Offers photo debit cards with personalization options.\n\nThe process typically involves:\n- Selecting a personalized card option\n- Uploading a high-resolution image\n- Paying a small additional fee\n- Waiting for card processing and delivery\n\nTo get the most current information and specific details, I recommend:\n- Checking the bank's official website\n- Visiting a local branch\n- Calling the bank's customer service\n\nNote that availability and specific terms might vary, so it's best to confirm directly with the bank.",
